    <string-array name="act_home_text_intro">
        <item>"PyjaBank is a demonstrator on the theme of security application development.\n\n"</item>
        <item>"For the example, we will handle simulated bank data. \"Your\" data is stored in an encrypted database (bdd).\n\n"</item>
        <item>"If you connect with an empty database, the username used will be saved and used as a reference.\n\n"</item>
        <item>"There can only be one registered user: to reset their information, empty the database. You can empty it at any time.\n\n"</item>
        <item>"Data recovery goes through a rest API, with an encrypted connection verified by certificate.\n\n"</item>
        <item>"Screenshots are not allowed on the app to ensure the confidentiality of this information.\n\n"</item>
        <item>"Once logged in, exiting the application in any way (screen off, return to the home screen, open applications) will automatically log you out.\n\n"</item>
        <item>"The language used by the application depends on your phone settings (English by default)."</item>
    </string-array>


